ective 12/14/2015.     Date: 2009-01-01Action: RevisionComments: Revised to provide faculty greater flexibility in designing and delivering their courses. Effective 01/01/2009.     Date: 2003-07-01Action: Revision     Date: 1999-06-01Action: Revision     Date: 1995-08-01Action: Revision    Top                          Main Menu Home FAQ Policy manual Resources Policy updates About the Policy Office  University Links  MyUNT Blackboard EagleConnect UNT Directory UNT Map UNT Calendar Jobs at UNT Give to UNT  Email & Phone   policy@unt.edu  940-565-4535    University Policy Office    Find UNT on Google Maps   1155 Union Circle #311277           Denton, Texas 76203-5017   Visitor Information  Call us Email Us UNT Map               Apply now Schedule a tour Get more info   Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy | Electronic Accessibility | Required Links | UNT Home ©2017 University of North Texas Required Links         
